## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c7256-285">Im folgenden Beispiel werden die Eigenschaften <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> und <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> der <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>-Klasse veranschaulicht.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c7256-285">The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> and <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> properties of the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c7256-286">In diesem Beispiel werden die benutzerdefinierten <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> und die <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A> der gesamten <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>abgerufen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c7256-286">This example gets the user-specified <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> and the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A> of all its <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Dim myADSPath As String = _  
      "LDAP://onecity/CN=Users,DC=onecity,DC=corp,DC=fabrikam,DC=com"  
  
' Create an Instance of DirectoryEntry.  
